text: BREAKING CHANGE: Replaced `initialState` with `init`, a function. This only affects new cassettes. Consult HELP for more information.
BREAKING CHANGE: Renamed `actor.name` to `actor.id`. This only applies if you're have an `actors` array in `initialState`. If so, please update your cassettes.
Added LOGIN/LOGOUT buttons (under the top-left SCRIPT-8 menu button). If you don't see your cassettes in SHELF, please LOGIN.
Renamed `tile` to `getTile`. Please update your cassettes. See HELP for more details.
